{"data":{"result":{"callId":"chatcmpl-tool-a8a7d49daf78f10e","kind":"tool-result","output":{"content":"1: # Runbook: Restart checkout-service\n2: \n3: **Trigger:** Elevated 5xx on `/v1/checkout` for >5 minutes.\n4: \n5: ## Steps\n6: \n7: 1. Confirm blast radius — check error rate in logs (grep `checkout-service` + `ERROR`).\n8: 2. Verify dependency — `payments-service` circuit breaker state.\n9: 3. **HITL** — Notify #incidents channel with summary before restart.\n10: 4. Drain traffic — scale checkout-service replicas to 0 (or enable maintenance mode).\n11: 5. Restart `payments-service` if circuit breaker is OPEN >60s.\n12: 6. Scale checkout back up; watch health for 10 minutes.\n13: 7. Document timeline in incident ticket.\n14: \n15: **Rollback:** Re-enable previous deployment tag if errors persist after restart.","path":"/workspace/runbook-restart-service.md","totalLines":15,"truncated":false},"toolName":"read_file"},"sequence":0,"stepIndex":0,"status":"completed","turnId":"turn_0"},"type":"action.result","meta":{"at":"2026-06-18T16:24:07.845Z"}}
